{
  "$schema": "https://json-schema.org/draft/2020-12/schema",
  "$id": "https://arcane-equilibrium.local/schemas/learning_runtime_choice_receipt_target_host_v1.schema.json",
  "title": "learning_runtime_choice_receipt_target_host_v1",
  "description": "Canonical self-hashed receipt emitted by target_host_probe_v1 (AIML LR0C, S1.6B). It is the TARGET-HOST variant of learning_runtime_choice_receipt_v1: the choice is re-made on REAL non-root Linux target-host (trade-core) evidence rather than the S1.6 Mac disposable stand-in. For candidate B (content_addressed_fixed_path) each seam is exercised with real non-root user-scope primitives (systemd-run --user --scope lifecycle, cgroup cpu/mem/pids enforcement, bwrap private-netns egress denial, bwrap native-lib load with bundle-only /proc/self/maps origin, content-addressed bundle + atomic pointer swap, kill/restart/teardown with an independent residue check); each carries verdict PASSED_TARGET_HOST or (honestly) DEFERRED_TARGET_HOST. For candidate A (exact_image_id_oci) every seam is NON_SATISFIABLE_NON_ROOT: trade-core has only a rootful docker daemon and LR2 forbids the OCI socket surface. The machine rule oci_selectable == (target_host_probe_performed AND every OCI seam PASSED_TARGET_HOST) runs on real evidence and is const false, so final_choice is content_addressed_fixed_path. binding is BINDING only when EVERY fixed-path seam is PASSED_TARGET_HOST; if any is not (today: PG-identity DEFERRED because postgresql-server is not installed on trade-core) binding is PROVISIONAL_PENDING_LINUX and pending_seams names the exact unmet seams. The applier alone cannot mark the independent_postcheck seam PASSED: run_target_host_probe emits it DEFERRED (a self-run receipt is PROVISIONAL naming independent_postcheck), and only a DISTINCT OPS verifier's attach_independent_postcheck with a real on-host residue observation (units/cgroup/netns/temp all gone) upgrades it to PASSED and re-derives BINDING. host_identity records BOTH expected_host and the REAL observed_host (os.uname().nodename); preflight fail-closes when they differ and the validator rejects observed_host != expected_host, so a non-target box cannot mint a trade-core receipt. HONESTY GATE: status==PASS REQUIRES evidence_class==PLATFORM_OR_EXTERNAL_ATTESTED and boundary.real_target_host_primitives_invoked==true, and require_target_host_attested additionally REQUIRES an EMBEDDED governed on-host command_capture_v2 artifact under target_host_capture (schema_version==command_capture_v2, a non-empty capturer node_id+native_agent, and record_digest == target_host_capture_digest so the digest and artifact cannot be decoupled) — a bare self-reported digest or evidence_class cannot certify the target-host exit. Offline structural acceptance of that artifact is NOT authentication (CLAUDE.md); the embedded artifact is what an out-of-band trusted host replays to authenticate. A Mac author cannot self-produce trade-core kernel facts, so a Mac structural synthesis is evidence_class==STRUCTURAL_ONLY and status==FAIL: it exercises the receipt/verdict LOGIC only and can never masquerade as the real target-host exit. The BINDING gate, OCI-non-satisfiable rule, pending_seams match, delegated-controller superset, applier!=verifier, and secret-scan are enforced in the delegated Python validator, not schema if/then. self_digest proves integrity, not authenticity (CLAUDE.md Typed Authority Matrix): a consumer accepting this as the S1-exit MUST re-run the probe on trade-core or obtain the governed on-host capture, and re-fetch the bound S1.1/S1.4/S1.5 dependencies by digest.",
  "type": "object",
  "additionalProperties": false,
  "required": [
    "schema_version",
    "harness_id",
    "status",
    "caller",
    "target_class",
    "evidence_class",
    "host_identity",
    "platform",
    "probe_scope",
    "candidate_probes",
    "selection",
    "unselected_path_removal",
    "production_running_attested",
    "target_host_capture_digest",
    "target_host_capture",
    "dependency_receipts",
    "boundary",
    "source_sha256",
    "schema_sha256",
    "secret_scan",
    "observation_time",
    "expires_at",
    "ttl_seconds",
    "failure_reason",
    "self_digest"
  ],
  "properties": {
    "schema_version": {"const": "learning_runtime_choice_receipt_target_host_v1"},
    "harness_id": {"const": "target_host_probe_v1"},
    "status": {"enum": ["PASS", "FAIL"]},
    "caller": {"type": "string", "minLength": 1},
    "target_class": {"const": "target_host"},
    "evidence_class": {"enum": ["PLATFORM_OR_EXTERNAL_ATTESTED", "STRUCTURAL_ONLY"]},
    "host_identity": {
      "type": "object",
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": [
        "expected_host",
        "observed_host",
        "non_root_uid",
        "passwordless_sudo_present",
        "delegated_controllers",
        "deferred_root_only_controllers",
        "throwaway_root_under_runtime_dir"
      ],
      "properties": {
        "expected_host": {"type": "string", "minLength": 1},
        "observed_host": {"type": "string", "minLength": 1},
        "non_root_uid": {"const": true},
        "passwordless_sudo_present": {"const": false},
        "delegated_controllers": {
          "type": "array",
          "minItems": 3,
          "items": {"type": "string", "minLength": 1}
        },
        "deferred_root_only_controllers": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {"enum": ["cpuset", "io", "hugetlb", "rdma"]}
        },
        "throwaway_root_under_runtime_dir": {"const": true}
      }
    },
    "platform": {
      "type": "object",
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": [
        "os",
        "arch",
        "python_version",
        "systemd_run_available",
        "bwrap_available",
        "non_root_oci_runtime_available"
      ],
      "properties": {
        "os": {"enum": ["darwin", "linux"]},
        "arch": {"type": "string", "minLength": 1},
        "python_version": {"type": "string", "minLength": 1},
        "systemd_run_available": {"type": "boolean"},
        "bwrap_available": {"type": "boolean"},
        "non_root_oci_runtime_available": {"const": false}
      }
    },
    "probe_scope": {
      "type": "object",
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": [
        "effect_class",
        "target_host_probe_performed",
        "adapter_id",
        "pg_identity_mode"
      ],
      "properties": {
        "effect_class": {"const": "TARGET_HOST_DISPOSABLE_RUNTIME_PROBE"},
        "target_host_probe_performed": {"type": "boolean"},
        "adapter_id": {"const": "learning_runtime_deploy_adapter_v1"},
        "pg_identity_mode": {"enum": ["deferred_server_absent", "real_initdb_cluster"]}
      }
    },
    "candidate_probes": {
      "type": "array",
      "minItems": 2,
      "items": {
        "type": "object",
        "additionalProperties": false,
        "required": [
          "candidate_id",
          "runtime_identity_kind",
          "apply_actor_node",
          "postcheck_verifier_node",
          "seams",
          "caveats"
        ],
        "properties": {
          "candidate_id": {"enum": ["exact_image_id_oci", "content_addressed_fixed_path"]},
          "runtime_identity_kind": {"enum": ["exact_image_id", "content_addressed_path"]},
          "apply_actor_node": {"type": "string", "minLength": 1},
          "postcheck_verifier_node": {"type": "string", "minLength": 1},
          "seams": {
            "type": "array",
            "minItems": 8,
            "items": {
              "type": "object",
              "additionalProperties": false,
              "required": ["seam_id", "verdict", "evidence_digest", "note"],
              "properties": {
                "seam_id": {"type": "string", "minLength": 1},
                "verdict": {"enum": ["PASSED_TARGET_HOST", "DEFERRED_TARGET_HOST", "NON_SATISFIABLE_NON_ROOT"]},
                "evidence_digest": {"$ref": "#/$defs/digest"},
                "note": {"type": "string", "minLength": 1},
                "representativeness": {"enum": ["representative_native_lib", "lr2_sealed_closure"]}
              }
            }
          },
          "caveats": {"type": "array", "items": {"type": "string", "minLength": 1}}
        }
      }
    },
    "selection": {
      "type": "object",
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": [
        "final_choice",
        "selection_rule",
        "oci_selectable",
        "binding",
        "pending_seams",
        "reason"
      ],
      "properties": {
        "final_choice": {"enum": ["content_addressed_fixed_path", "exact_image_id_oci"]},
        "selection_rule": {"const": "oci_only_if_all_seams_pass_else_fixed_path"},
        "oci_selectable": {"const": false},
        "binding": {"enum": ["BINDING", "PROVISIONAL_PENDING_LINUX"]},
        "pending_seams": {"type": "array", "items": {"type": "string", "minLength": 1}},
        "reason": {"type": "string", "minLength": 1}
      }
    },
    "unselected_path_removal": {
      "type": "object",
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": [
        "unselected_candidate",
        "unselected_production_artifact_present",
        "production_path_removed",
        "forecloses_downstream",
        "note"
      ],
      "properties": {
        "unselected_candidate": {"const": "exact_image_id_oci"},
        "unselected_production_artifact_present": {"const": false},
        "production_path_removed": {"const": true},
        "forecloses_downstream": {"const": true},
        "note": {"type": "string", "minLength": 1}
      }
    },
    "production_running_attested": {"const": false},
    "target_host_capture_digest": {"anyOf": [{"$ref": "#/$defs/digest"}, {"type": "null"}]},
    "target_host_capture": {
      "anyOf": [
        {"type": "null"},
        {
          "type": "object",
          "required": ["schema_version", "record_digest", "node_id", "native_agent"],
          "properties": {
            "schema_version": {"const": "command_capture_v2"},
            "record_digest": {"$ref": "#/$defs/digest"},
            "node_id": {"type": "string", "minLength": 1},
            "native_agent": {"type": "string", "minLength": 1},
            "role_id": {"type": "string", "minLength": 1}
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    "dependency_receipts": {
      "type": "object",
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": [
        "runtime_candidate_receipt_a_digest",
        "runtime_candidate_receipt_b_digest",
        "runtime_candidate_comparison_digest",
        "effect_seams_ready_receipt_digest",
        "component_effect_matrix_digest",
        "pg_readonly_identity_receipt_digest"
      ],
      "properties": {
        "runtime_candidate_receipt_a_digest": {"$ref": "#/$defs/digest"},
        "runtime_candidate_receipt_b_digest": {"$ref": "#/$defs/digest"},
        "runtime_candidate_comparison_digest": {"$ref": "#/$defs/digest"},
        "effect_seams_ready_receipt_digest": {"$ref": "#/$defs/digest"},
        "component_effect_matrix_digest": {"$ref": "#/$defs/digest"},
        "pg_readonly_identity_receipt_digest": {"$ref": "#/$defs/digest"}
      }
    },
    "boundary": {
      "type": "object",
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": [
        "non_root",
        "user_scope_only",
        "no_docker_invoked",
        "no_system_scope",
        "no_production_path",
        "prod_pg_untouched",
        "applier_ne_verifier",
        "production_running_attested",
        "real_target_host_primitives_invoked",
        "complete_teardown_verified"
      ],
      "properties": {
        "non_root": {"const": true},
        "user_scope_only": {"const": true},
        "no_docker_invoked": {"const": true},
        "no_system_scope": {"const": true},
        "no_production_path": {"const": true},
        "prod_pg_untouched": {"const": true},
        "applier_ne_verifier": {"const": true},
        "production_running_attested": {"const": false},
        "real_target_host_primitives_invoked": {"type": "boolean"},
        "complete_teardown_verified": {"type": "boolean"}
      }
    },
    "source_sha256": {"$ref": "#/$defs/digest"},
    "schema_sha256": {"$ref": "#/$defs/digest"},
    "secret_scan": {
      "type": "object",
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": ["patterns_checked", "leaked"],
      "properties": {
        "patterns_checked": {"type": "array", "minItems": 1, "items": {"type": "string", "minLength": 1}},
        "leaked": {"const": false}
      }
    },
    "observation_time": {"$ref": "#/$defs/timestamp"},
    "expires_at": {"$ref": "#/$defs/timestamp"},
    "ttl_seconds": {"type": "integer", "minimum": 1, "maximum": 3600},
    "failure_reason": {"anyOf": [{"type": "string", "minLength": 1}, {"type": "null"}]},
    "self_digest": {"$ref": "#/$defs/digest"}
  },
  "allOf": [
    {
      "if": {"properties": {"status": {"const": "PASS"}}},
      "then": {
        "properties": {
          "evidence_class": {"const": "PLATFORM_OR_EXTERNAL_ATTESTED"},
          "failure_reason": {"type": "null"},
          "probe_scope": {
            "properties": {"target_host_probe_performed": {"const": true}}
          },
          "selection": {
            "properties": {
              "final_choice": {"const": "content_addressed_fixed_path"},
              "oci_selectable": {"const": false}
            }
          },
          "boundary": {
            "properties": {
              "real_target_host_primitives_invoked": {"const": true},
              "complete_teardown_verified": {"const": true}
            }
          }
        }
      },
      "else": {
        "properties": {
          "failure_reason": {"type": "string", "minLength": 1}
        }
      }
    }
  ],
  "$defs": {
    "digest": {"type": "string", "pattern": "^sha256:[0-9a-f]{64}$"},
    "timestamp": {"type": "string", "format": "date-time"}
  }
}
